      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为GUI工具设计一个类结构。核心是一个TabTemplate，它作为所有标签页设置的基类，然后TabSettings会继承它。另外，TabSettings需要组合一个Model对象来管理数据状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabTemplate",
        "TabSettings",
        "Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到TabTemplate和Model应该放在不同的命名空间里？TabTemplate属于guitool，Model放在rotgui下会更合理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "guitool",
        "rotgui",
        "TabTemplate",
        "Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，guitool放界面相关的类，rotgui放模型层的类。TabSettings作为具体实现，继承TabTemplate，同时聚合Model。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "guitool",
        "rotgui",
        "TabTemplate",
        "TabSettings",
        "Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出结构：guitool命名空间包含TabTemplate，rotgui包含Model，TabSettings继承TabTemplate，并用组合关系连接Model。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "guitool",
        "rotgui",
        "TabTemplate",
        "TabSettings",
        "Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，TabSettings和Model的关系应该是强组合，Model的生命周期由TabSettings管理，不是普通的聚合。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabSettings",
        "Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我把TabSettings到Model的连线改成实心菱形，表示组合关系。这样TabSettings销毁时Model也会一起销毁。",
      "elements_involved": [
